Write a get and post method in nodejs using http package and do the followings 

1.Get the user details such as name,age,phone,city,address using post man 
2.Store this details inside the txt file using fs package .
3.Write the get method and bring that file to frontend to display the result 
3.please do the following validation before saving to file 
   name - must be required 
   age - must be greater then 18 
   phone - required 
   city - required 
   address - required 
4.if any validation error happens send the 400 error code alone with particular field error message.
